    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thx. i mean i get the basics, but like, given how much we're seeing with extreme weather and stuff lately, is there any way we can actually meet carbon goals without it? or is the debate kind of a distraction if nuclear is basically the only way to get that much power fast enough?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
